---
import ShareableQuote from "../../ShareableQuote.astro";
---

<section
    id="cuerpos-rotos"
    class="wheat-relative wheat-font-serif wheat-min-h-screen wheat-flex wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-py-12 wheat-py-24@md wheat-skeleton-section"
>
    <div class="wheat-container wheat-container--wide wheat-px-6">
        <div class="wheat-text-center wheat-mb-12 wheat-mb-16@md">
            <span class="trigo-chapter wheat-skeleton-chapter wheat-text-xs wheat-text-sm@md wheat-tracking-widest wheat-uppercase">
                El Coste Biológico
            </span>
            <h2 class="wheat-text-3xl wheat-text-4xl@md wheat-font-bold wheat-mt-4 wheat-skeleton-title">Cuerpos rotos</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="wheat-grid wheat-grid--cols-2 wheat-items-center wheat-gap-12">
            <div class="wheat-space-y-6 wheat-space-y-8@md">
                <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-skeleton-text">
                    <ShareableQuote
                        quote="El cuerpo humano evolucionó durante 2 millones de años para trepar, correr y cazar. No para agacharse, cavar y cargar piedras."
                    />
                </p>
                <p class="wheat-text-base wheat-text-lg@md wheat-leading-relaxed wheat-skeleton-text">
                    La adopción de la agricultura trajo una plaga de dolencias nuevas: hernias,
                    artritis, y deformaciones de la columna. Pero lo peor estaba en los huesos.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="wheat-relative wheat-skeleton-card wheat-p-4 wheat-rounded-lg wheat-flex wheat-flex-col wheat-items-center wheat-justify-center wheat-overflow-hidden">
                <img
                    src="/images/concepts/trigo/skeleton-compare.webp"
                    alt="Comparación de esqueletos: Cazador vs Agricultor"
                    class="wheat-w-full wheat-h-auto wheat-rounded wheat-skeleton-img"
                />
                <div class="wheat-mt-4 wheat-text-center wheat-font-mono wheat-skeleton-caption">
                    FIG. 2: PALEOPATOLOGÍA COMPARADA (Cohen & Armelagos, 1984)
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .wheat-skeleton-section {
        color: #e7e5e4;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(120, 53, 4, 0.1);
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-chapter {
        color: #a8a29e;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-title {
        color: #e7e5e4;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-text {
        color: #d6d3d1;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-card {
        background-color: #1c1917;
        border: 1px solid #292524;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-img {
        box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        opacity: 0.9;
        transition: opacity 0.5s;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-img:hover {
        opacity: 1;
    }
    .wheat-skeleton-caption {
        font-size: 10px;
        color: #57534e;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .wheat-mb-16\@md {
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .wheat-space-y-8\@md > * + * {
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
    }
</style>
